SCREAMING happy birthday to my Wonder ✨Woman @mshogg . You have done nothing but be the best mother you could be ❤️‍🔥😍and more. I am forever grateful to have someone who supports me and believes in me as much 🙏🏽🫂as you do. There would be no career if it wasn’t for your sacrifice, determination and love❤️‍🔥. There are so many moments where I feel like I can’t and you forever remind me that I can 🙌🏽and will. Even before I even wanted to be a entertainer you saw something in me that was special ✨from young. Thank you for always being my rock when I need you and know I will always 😍😭be here for you when you need me. It’s been amazing growing as an adult and even greater 🙏🏽being able to learn, Support and grow together as mother and son. Truly a bond that can’t be 🤞🏽broken and I want you to know how much I love and Appreciate you for all that you do and 🤟🏽continue to do for me and brother.
•
A few of my favorite things about you first is how unapologetic you are. 🙌🏽You are fearless, there is nothing on this earth you will not seek out and find. You will move mountains if that is what it takes and I truly admire that quality about you. I love how much you truly love and 😝want to have a good time wherever you go. I think that is a trait I got from you lol. When you walk into a room not only do you brighten ☀️it with your smile but you breath life with your personality. Another favorite is how you move 😊to the beat of your own drum. You will go to a concert by yourself if you have to, nothing will stop you from fulfilling on your plan or having a good time. Lastly, as I previously mentioned is the personality. You are truly 😂🤣funny and I don’t know if you mean to be however, you got jokes young lady. It keeps me on my toes FOR SURE.
•
I love you and I could go on for days. 🥰I wanted you to know in words how special you are and there’s only one you and I’m thankful/blessed 🥳God chose you to be my mom so happy birthday and to many many many more birthdays to come.✨
